  "texts": [
    "The Use of experience category was the next most evaluated (18.5%) and it was used to investigate user opinions on the use of the devices and applications (Usability topic), and to find out whether they enjoyed it (Satisfaction topic).",
    "It was included in most fields, as the user opinions are important to improve the applications and experience.",
    "In contrast, the Virtual Reality features topic was less common (14.6%).",
    "In this category, iVR aspects such as the feeling of presence, the sense of immersion, and level of realism were evaluated.",
    "The assessment of those features meant that the quality of the iVR experience could be verified in relation to whether it was sufficient to meet the objectives."
  ],
